snippet.title: Behind the Curtain
snippet.description:
Behind the Curtain crafts educational video essays using the most valuable insights from professionals in the industry. Take a look into the creative processes of the Coen Brothers, Quentin Tarantino, the creators of The Office, and many more!

Behind the Curtain focuses on two things:
1) Learning from professionals
2) Growing in a community of filmmakers as passionate as you

Being a member means being held accountable to become a better writer.
